<h3>Secondary Analysis</h3>

<p>
Our interactive analysis software allows the user to helps to perform subsequent 
data analysis such as quantification (counting), and it helps to project results 
back into the images, either highlighting individual transcripts, combinations of 
genes or whole gene-sets to map transcription patterns onto morphological structures. 
A colocalization matrix is determined and presented as a dendrogram or heatmap. 
Results can be exported in publication-ready quality.
</p>

